## Your First Machine

Let's write a simple function that prints a welcome message.

```dart
// creating the function
void sayHello() {
  print('Welcome to the game!');
}

void main() {
  // Using (calling) the function!
  sayHello(); 
}
```
To use a function, you just type its name followed by `();`.

